Source: jp4-tools
Section: graphics
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Paulo Henrique Silva <ph.silva@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 7), scons, pkg-config, libavcodec-dev,
               libavformat-dev, libexpat1-dev, libexif-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.4
Homepage: http://wiki.elphel.com/index.php?title=jp4-tools

Package: jp4-tools
Architecture: i386 amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libavcodec52 | libavcodec-unstripped-52,
         libavformat52 | libavformat-unstripped-52, libexpat1, libexif12
Description: Image and video processing tools for Elphel's JP4 format.
 This package contains tools to work with Elphel's (http://www.elphel.com) 
 images and videos in JP4 format.
 jp4-convert is capable of transform a JP4 movie/image in a few different formats,
 including Adobe's Digital Negative Format (DNG).
